(10, 0, 4, 'Chairman', 'chairman', '<p><span style="font-family: helvetica; font-size: medium;">Events here and around the world make everyday a challenge for the common Filipino. Escalating price</span><span style="font-family: helvetica; font-size: medium;">s in oil and commodities squeeze household budgets. Wages couldn&rsquo;t cover necessities, let alone encourage people to save. And the job market becomes more competitive as employers</span><span style="font-family: helvetica; font-size: medium;"> seek better qualifications.</span></p>\r\n<p><span style="font-family: helvetica; font-size: medium;"><img style="float: left; margin-right: 10px;" title="Chairman" src="../../../assets/media/uploads/Chairmans-Message-2011_21-358x1024.png" alt="Chairman" width="161" height="456" /></span><span style="font-family: helvetica; font-size: medium;">Times are hard and we Filipinos do our best to get by with the grace of </span><span style="font-family: helvetica; font-size: medium;">God and sheer perseverance. We</span><span style="font-family: helvetica; font-size: medium;"> can weather any storm. All we need is a chance to prove we can do it.</span></p>\r\n<p><span style="font-family: helvetica; font-size: medium;">Vital C Health Products, Inc. believes in giving Filipinos from all walks of life an opportunity to </span><span style="font-family: helvetica; font-size: medium;">achieve financial freedom. This means being able to earn a clean and sufficient living for your family. To one day be able to buy a house and a car. To be debt-free. To eventually travel abroad and save for the future.</span></p>\r\n<p><span style="font-family: helvetica; font-size: medium;">These dreams may seem elusive especially to those who are living from paycheck to paycheck. But some of our members have already achieved these dreams and many are on their way. And no, they didn&rsquo;t come from privilege. They too came from humble beginnings. Some haven&rsquo;t even gone to college. They all started small until they grew their downlines through hard work, patience and sheer determination.</span></p>\r\n<p><span style="font-family: helvetica; font-size: medium;">At Vital C, we empower our members to go beyond expectations. Our excellent line of beauty and wellness products works so well that it&rsquo;s easy to stand by them and share them with as many people as possible. Our proactive management offers training and support through various initiatives and activities. Our team leaders work hard to inspire and motivate. And we continue to innovate so we can deliver exciting and highly beneficial products that will lead to your success.</span></p>\r\n<p><span style="font-family: helvetica; font-size: medium;">With open arms and open hearts, we welcome you to the Vital C family.</span></p>\r\n<p><span style="font-family: helvetica; font-size: medium;">Together, we can do great things.</span></p>', '', '', 1, '', 'page', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '2012-07-06 21:26:07'),
(11, 0, 4, 'Management', 'management', '<p>Owners of the company have combined years of proven records of accomplishments;<br /> as successful businessmen in the field of:</p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li style="list-style-type: none;"><em>39 years in Real Estate Development,</em></li>\r\n<li style="list-style-type: none;"><em>15 years in infrastructure,</em></li>\r\n<li style="list-style-type: none;"><em>38 years in Cargo Forwarding,</em></li>\r\n<li style="list-style-type: none;"><em>20 years in Hotel and</em></li>\r\n<li style="list-style-type: none;"><em>19 years in the Food Chain Industry.</em></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p>Being the only Filipino-owned Company, Vital C possesses a highly-competitive Management team with combined</p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li style="list-style-type: none;"><em>67 years of skill in excellent Systems and Administrative </em>expertise as well as combined</li>\r\n<li style="list-style-type: none;"><em>30 years of experience in Network and Sales Marketing.</em></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p>The Vital C Medical Board as well has vast experience in the practice of mainstream medicine, research &amp; laboratory testing for 41 years.</p>\r\n<p>Vital C is the only Filipino-owned company that owns its corporate office and operates three company-owned Depots serving the main lands: Luzon, Visayas and Mindanao.</p>', '', '', 1, '', 'page', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '2012-07-12 08:55:02'),
(12, 0, 4, 'Members', 'members', '<p>Vital C has produced more than <em>70,000 distributors since it launched in 2008</em>. The<em> International Group Points System Marketing Program (IGPSM)</em> is numbering to a total number of consumers with more than 100,000 users.</p>\r\n<p>Vital C has already produced <em>8 Exclusive Product Centers</em> and <em>150 International Mobile Franchisees (IMF) </em>nationwide with sales with more than <em>Php100M </em>in a span of one year alone.</p>\r\n<p>Vital C had already sent 200 Distributors in an all-expense paid trip to Hong Kong (2008), Bangkok (2009) and Macau (2011).</p>\r\n<p>Vital C has a total of <em>thirty-four (34) Millionaires&rsquo; Club members</em> by the first half of 2012. The previous year also produced <em>a total of</em><em> eight (8) members</em> of the prestigious, <em>Vital C President&rsquo;s Club</em> and as of this date, <em>four (4) members </em>are awarded as the <em>Grand Master&rsquo;s of Vital C.</em></p>\r\n<p>Truly, Vital C is Beyond Excellence.</p>', '', '', 1, '', 'page', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '2012-07-12 08:56:40'),
(13, 0, 4, 'Certifications', 'awards-and-certificates', '<h2>Licenses and Certifications of Vital C Health Products:</h2>\r\n<h3 style="color: #669933;"><strong>Halal Certifications</strong></h3>\r\n<hr style="color: #669933;" />\r\n<p style="text-align: center;"><strong><a style="border: none; background: none; margin: 0 2px 0 2px;" href="../../../assets/media/uploads/HALAL-seal_corrected2.png"><img style="border: 0px initial initial;" title="HALAL-seal_corrected" src="../../../assets/media/uploads/HALAL-seal_corrected2.png" alt="" width="90" height="90" /></a><br /> </strong></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: center;"><a href="../../../assets/media/uploads/HALAL-VC.jpg"><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-3281" title="HALAL - VC" src="../../../assets/media/uploads/HALAL-VC.jpg" alt="" width="407" height="526" /></a></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: center;"><a href="../../../assets/media/uploads/HALAL-Vital-C.jpg"><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-3285" title="HALAL - Vital C" src="../../../assets/media/uploads/HALAL-Vital-C.jpg" alt="" width="406" height="525" /></a></p>\r\n<h3 style="color: #669933;"><strong>Vital C Products that use Veggie capsule capsules are also Kosher certified and Vegetarian Society Approved.</strong></h3>\r\n<hr style="color: #669933;" />\r\n<p style="text-align: center;"><strong><a href="../../../assets/media/uploads/kosher_certified_071.gif"><img class="size-full wp-image-239  aligncenter" title="kosher_certified_07" src="../../../assets/media/uploads/kosher_certified_071.gif" alt="" width="100" height="90" /></a><a href="../../../assets/media/uploads/logo_vegetarian_society1.gif"><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-237" title="logo_vegetarian_society" src="../../../assets/media/uploads/logo_vegetarian_society1.gif" alt="" width="91" height="90" /></a><br /> </strong></p>\r\n<h3 style="color: #669933;"><strong>Food And Drugs Authority Certification</strong></h3>\r\n<hr style="color: #669933;" />\r\n<p style="text-align: ce